casebody.data:
Third Department,

August 4,1987

(August 4, 1987) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Nasar Abdul Aziz, Also Known as Raymond Gilliard, Petitioner, v Eugene LeFevre, as Superintendent of Clinton Correctional Facility, Respondent.

Application, pursuant to CPLR 7002 (b) (2), for writ of habeas corpus denied (see, People ex rel. Davis v Coombe, 97 AD2d 667). Kane, J. P., Main, Casey, Weiss and Mikoll, JJ., concur.
